{"id": "1426638468116643882", "channel_id": "1426602446783909928", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "3 options I run:\n\nLiz + Lily and:\n\n1. Clem + Castor for a Arc 2 main team first pass - This team is very tanky and will win the level, but may take a lot of rounds.\n2. Horla + GDoll - This team is exalt heavy and will help you get a 10 turn or less pass on main story, but it requires more navigation\n3. Ogier + Erica - This is for DTides as then you are not using other high value units (like clem or horla).\n\nAnd you can always mix and match those units above.\n\nI am hoping that the new Ultra unit will help a Liz team.....but we shall see.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T18:31:56.460000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["244719977314123776"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "blobthanks", "emoji_id": "825444835460644929", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1426624618990403597", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426602446783909928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Standard Tier List - Early and Endgame", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1395992270880243753", "1304022948000043028", "1304023032297160735"]}
